I just enabled Pep easing[1] on the open source version of PrimaryWall[2]. Easing is basically where the notes decellerate into place, making them have a much smoother move across the screen.

Using pep[3] meant I can remove jquery UI which is a really overweight framework to include so hopefully page load will be faster too :) Over the next few months I will be optimizing page load and including more bug monitoring and hopefully updating the PrimaryWall.com version.[4]

Enjoy :)

